# UISketch Dataset

A large-scale dataset of 19,000 hand-drawn sketches of 21 UI element categories collected from 1,218 participants, including UI/UX designers, front-end developers, HCI, and CS grad students

## Citation

```bibtex
@inbook{uisketch,
	title        = {UISketch: A Large-Scale Dataset of UI Element Sketches},
	author       = {Sermuga Pandian, Vinoth Pandian and Suleri, Sarah and Jarke, Prof. Dr. Matthias},
	year         = 2021,
	booktitle    = {Proceedings of the 2021 CHI Conference on Human Factors in Computing Systems},
	publisher    = {Association for Computing Machinery},
	address      = {New York, NY, USA},
	isbn         = 9781450380966,
	url          = {https://doi.org/10.1145/3411764.3445784},
	articleno    = 319,
	numpages     = 14
}
```
---

> NOTE: **The models mentioned below were trained for a subset (17,979 sketches). Check [kaggle notebooks](https://www.kaggle.com/vinothpandian/code), specifically [ResNet 152 notebook](https://www.kaggle.com/vinothpandian/resnet-152) on how to reuse the weights mentioned below**
